" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>This is an <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;h1&gt;</code> tag</h1>\n<h2 id=\"this-is-an-h2-tag\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#this-is-an-h2-tag\" aria-label=\"this is an h2 tag permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>This is an <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;h2&gt;</code> tag</h2>\n<h6 id=\"this-is-an-h6-tag\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#this-is-an-h6-tag\" aria-label=\"this is an h6 tag permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>This is an <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;h6&gt;</code> tag</h6>\n<h1 id=\"heading-level-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#heading-level-1\" aria-label=\"heading level 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Heading level 1</h1>\n<h2 id=\"heading-level-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#heading-level-2\" aria-label=\"heading level 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Heading level 2</h2>\n<h2 id=\"for-emphasis\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#for-emphasis\" aria-label=\"for emphasis permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>For Emphasis</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"md\"><pre class=\"language-md\"><code class=\"language-md\"><span class=\"token italic\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">*</span><span class=\"token content\">This text will be italic</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">*</span></span>\n<span class=\"token italic\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">_</span><span class=\"token content\">This will also be italic</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">_</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token bold\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">**</span><span class=\"token content\">This text will be bold</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">**</span></span>\n<span class=\"token bold\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">__</span><span class=\"token content\">This will also be bold</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">__</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token bold\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">**</span><span class=\"token content\">This is on a separate line</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">**</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token italic\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">_</span><span class=\"token content\">You <span class=\"token bold\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">**</span><span class=\"token content\">can</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">**</span></span> combine them</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">_</span></span>\n<span class=\"token title important\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">#</span> _You **can** combine them_ but # needs to start at the first position to make it a h1 tag</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><em>This text will be italic</em>\n<em>This will also be italic</em></p>\n<p><strong>This text will be bold</strong>\n<strong>This will also be bold</strong></p>\n<p><strong>This is on a separate line</strong></p>\n<p><em>You <strong>can</strong> combine them</em></p>\n<h1 id=\"you-can-combine-them-but--needs-to-start-at-the-first-position-to-make-it-a-h1-tag\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#you-can-combine-them-but--needs-to-start-at-the-first-position-to-make-it-a-h1-tag\" aria-label=\"you can combine them but  needs to start at the first position to make i